'Cepat pergi ke sana.
Waktumu sangat sedikit.'

00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:28.080
'Gudan!'

00:13:54.440 --> 00:13:55.280
Sial!

00:13:55.720 --> 00:13:57.560
Apakah kamu terluka parah?

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:03.480
Maafkan aku, Shweta.

